10_2701 eːkasmin dineː yAːjYavalkyaH yaTAːpUːrvam upadeːzavAːcanaM kurvan AːsIːt .
10_2702 janakamahAːrAːjaH anyeː RSayaH ca zradDayAː zrRNvantaH Aːsan.
10_2703 tadAː eːva kazcana vaquH DAːvan tatra AːgatavAːn .
10_2704 RRSIːn uktavAːn ca-BoːH BoːH RSayaH BavatAːM kuqIːrAːNi agninAː jvalanti santi iti .
10_2705 parantu tad zrutvAː api yAːjYavalkyaH upadeːzaM taTAː eːva anuvartitavAːn .
10_2706 tadAː sarveː api RRSayaH Jaqiti utTAːya tatra DAːvitavantaH .
10_2707 jvalataH kuqIːrAːt svIːyAːni daNxa-kamaNxalu-mRgacarmAːdIːni vastUːni AːnIːtavantaH ca.
10_2708 itoː api upadeːzaH anuvartamAːnaH eːva AːsIːt .
10_2709 janaka-mahAːrAːjaH nizcalam upavizya zrRNvan AːsIːt.
10_2710 kiYcitakAːla anantaram anyaH kazcana tatra Aːgatya uktavAːn - praBoː! janakamahAːrAːja! miTilAːnagareː agnisparzaH jAːtaH asti .
10_2711 mahAːn anarTaH samBavati iti .
10_2712 parantu tad zrutvAː api janakamahAːrAːjaH kiYcid api vicalitaH na aBavat .
10_2713 saH yaTAːpUːrvam upadeːzaM zrRNvan eːva AːsIːt .
10_2714 tataH kiYcit kAːla anantaram aparaH Aːgatya uktavAːn- mahAːrAːja! aDunAː tu rAːjaBavanam api agninAː jvalati.
10_2715 BavataH antaHpuram api dahyamAːnam asti iti.
10_2716 aDunAː api janakamahAːrAːjaH avicalitaH san upadeːzazravaNeː eːva nirataH AːsIːt .
10_2717 tat pazcAːt yAːjYavalkyaH upadeːzaM samAːpitavAːn .
10_2718 tataH anyAːn RSIːn uktavAːn ca - BoːH RSayaH! kuqIːraM jvalati iti vAːrtAːM zrRtvAː viraktAːH api BavantaH tatra DAːvitvAː svIːyAːni vastUːni AːnIːtavantaH .
10_2719 parantu janakamahAːrAːjaH svasya nagaraM , Bavanam antaHpuraM ca jvalati iti vAːrtAːM zrutvAː api kiYcit api vicalitaH na aBavat .
10_2720 BavatAːM tasya ca eːtAːvAːn eːva BeːdaH .
10_2721 ataH eːva ahaM tasya Aːgamana anantaram eːva upadeːzasya AːramBaM karoːmi iti .
