10_2752 yadi kadAːcit mama BAːgyaM kSIːNaM BaviSyati tarhi kaTam ahaM jIːveːyam.
10_2753 api ca ,AːgAːmini janmani api idam eːva gRhaM, kSeːtraM,kuqumbaM,BAːryAː,putrAːH ca kiM mama BaveːyuH.
10_2754 eːtasyAːH samasyAːyAːH parihAːraH kaH.
