10_2760 tatra pravacanakartAː kazcit pravacanaM kurvan AːsIːt .
10_2761 saH avadat- BUːloːkeː sarvam anityam deːvAːH amRtasya seːvanAːt ciraYjIːvinaH nityasuKinaH ca Bavanti iti.
10_2762 idaM vacanaM kRSNacandrasya zroːtrayoːH patitam.
10_2763 tasya manasi upAːyaH kazcana utpannaH.
10_2764 yadi ahaM mat kuqumbajanAːH ca amRtaM seːveːmahi tarhi vayam api nityasuKina: BavituM zaknuyAːm Kalu.
10_2765 ataH saH nirNIːtavAːn yat mayAː indradarzanAːrTaM tapa: karaNIːyam iti.
10_2766 anantaradineː eːva saH samIːpasTaM vanaM gatavAːn .
10_2767 vaneː kutracit sTitvAː sarvAːNi suKAːni tyaktvAː kaVoːreː tapasi magnaH aBavat.
10_2768 eːteːna santuSqaH deːveːndraH kRSNacandrasya purataH pratyakSaH aBavat.
10_2769 amRtapUːrNaM Gaqam eːkaM tasmEː dattvAː saH - heː kRSNacandra ! BavantaH AːtRpti amRtaM pAːtum arhanti .
10_2770 parantu eːkaH niyamaH smartavyaH yat eːSaH GaqaH aDaH na sTAːpanIːyaH iti uktvAː antarhitaH jAːtaH.
10_2771 yadAː vanasya maDyaBAːgaH atIːtaH tadAː .
10_2772 kRSNacandreːNa zOːcazawkAː prAːptAː .
10_2773 taxAːgaH kazcana teːna samIːpeː dRSqaH.
10_2774 amRtaGaqaM kiM karoːmi.
10_2775 iti cintayan eːva saH paritaH dRSqiM prasAːritavAːn .
10_2776 tAːvatAː daridraH janaH kazcana tatra AːgatavAːn .
