10_2778 aDaH na sTAːpanIːyaH eːSaH.
10_2779 ataH yAːvat aham eːtasmin taxAːgeː snAːna AːdikaM kRtvAː prati AːgamiSyAːmi tAːvat BavatAː hasteːna eːva GaqaM gRhIːtvAː atra eːva sTAːtavyam iti uktvAː GaqaM tasya hasteː sTAːpayitvAː taxAːgaM gatavAːn.
10_2780 AːgataH manuSyaH tu atidaridraH udyoːgaH koː api na AːsIːt tasya .
10_2781 keːByazcit dineːByaH udaraveːdanAː api taM bahuDAː pIːxayati sma .
10_2782 vEːdyaM draSqum, OːSaDaM kreːtuM vAː tasya samIːpeː Danam api na AːsIːt .
10_2783 jIːvaneː viraktiM prAːptavAːn saH loːkeː mAːdRzasya jIːvanam asAːDyam.
10_2784 mama maraNam eːva ucitam iti nizcitya viSapadAːrTasya anveːSaNAːrTam eːva vanaM praviSqavAːn AːsIːt .
10_2785 akasmAːt kRSNacandreːNa dattaH viSaGaqaH amRtaGaqaHiva tasmEː pratIːyata .
