6_1676 gRhasya samAːn BAːgAːn kRtvAː catvAːroː BrAːtaraH tatra pRTag pRTak avasan .
6_1677 gRhapAːlasya ca viSayeː teː nirNIːtavantaH , asya gRhapAːlasya praTamaH pAːdaH DanarAːjasya, dvitIːyaH pAːdoː DanaganDasya, tRtIːyaH pAːdaH DanaprIːteːH,caturTazca pAːdaH DanaruceːH asti .
6_1678 asya pAːlanAːya poːSaNAːya ca yoːvyayoː Baveːt soː$smAːBiH sarvEːH kAːryaH .
6_1679 kadAːcit sa gRhapAːlaH DanaganDasya gRhaBAːgeː gatvAː dugDam apibat .
6_1680 saH eːtad apazyat .
6_1681 krudDoː BUːtvAː DanaganDoː daNxeːna gRhapAːlaM prAːharat .
6_1682 teːna gRhapAːlasya caturTaH pAːdaH kSataH .
6_1683 ataH tasya pAːdasya rakSakeːNa DanaruciNAː tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna pUːrNam vastraKaNxaM kSateː pAːdeː badDam .
6_1684 akasmAːt tasmAːt agneːH sPuliwgAː utpatitAːH tEːH sPuliwgEːH gRhapAːlasya kSateː pAːdeː badDaM vastraKaNxaM jvalayitum AːraBata .
6_1685 gRhapAːloː BIːtaH san itastataH aDAːvat .
6_1686 yAːvad agniH sarveːSu gRhaBAːgeːSu prAːrasat tAːvaccatvAːroː BrAːtaroː yAːvad gRhIːtuM zakyaM tAːvad gRhIːtvAː gRhAːd nirgatAːH .
6_1687 zIːGrameːva sarvaM gRham adahat .
6_1688 krudDAːsteː eːSa tavAːparAːDoː$sti eːSa tavAːparAːDoː$sti iti kaTayantaH kalaham akurvan .
6_1689 tataH DanaruciH triBiH BrAːtRBiH badDaH .
6_1690 trayoː BrAːtaraH DanaruciM badDvAː nyAːyAːlayaM anayan .
6_1691 tAːn dRSqvAː nyAːyAːDIːzoː$vadat-yUːyaM sarveː aBiyoːktAːraH sTa eːSa ca badDaH puruSoː$Biyukta iti pratiBAːti .
6_1692 keː yUːyam eːSa badDaH puruSoː$mAːkaM kaniSVoː BrAːtAː asti .
6_1693 gRhadAːhasya eːSa eːva karaNam .
6_1694 ata eːva daNxamahati .
6_1695 nyAːyAːDIːzoː$vadat-heː aBiyoːktAːraH ! aham aparAːDam ajYAːtvAː ,aparAːDasya pramAːNam alabDvAː ,aBiyuktasya aBiyoːktRNAːM ca yuktIːH azrutvAː na kamapi daNxayAːmi .
6_1696 kaTayata,ka eːtasya aBiyuktAːsyAːparAːDaH .
6_1697 tadAː DanaganDoː$vadat-eːSaH gRhamadahat.
6_1698 nyAːyAːDIːzaH apRcCat-kaTam.
6_1699 aparAːDasya kiM pramAːNam .
6_1700 kAː vAː yuSmAːkaM yuktiH .
6_1701 tasya praTamasya pAːdasya rakSakaH jyeːSVoː BrAːtAː, dvitIːyasya pAːdasya DanaganDaH, tRtIːyasya pAːdasya ahaM caturTasya ca pAːdasya eːSa DanaruciH akSakoː nirDAːritaH .
6_1702 yadAː gRhapAːlasya caturTeː pAːdeː kSatam aBavat tadAː aneːna tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna pUːrNaM vastraKaNxaM tasya caturTeː pAːdeː badDam .
6_1703 tadanantaraM vastraKaNxaM ajvalayat .
6_1704 BIːtaH san gRhapAːlaH itastataH aDAːvat sarvaM gRhaM adahat .
6_1705 ataH gRhapAːlasya caturTaH pAːdoː gRhadAːhasya kAːraNam .
6_1706 tasya pAːdasya rakSakaH eːSaH kaniSVaH BrAːtAː gRhadAːhasya karttAː asti .
6_1707 ataeːva eːSa daNxanIːyaH .
6_1708 eːteːna asmAːkaM hAːniH pUːraNIːyAː.
6_1709 nyAːyAːDIːzoː$BiyuktamapRcCat-kimeːtat satyam .
6_1710 kaniSVoː BrAːtAː avadat-mAːnanIːya !ahaM caturTasya pAːdasya rakSakoː$smi iti satyam .
6_1711 tasmin pAːdeː tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna pUːrNaM vastraKaNxaM mayAː badDaM iti satyam .
6_1712 vastraKaNxam ajvalad ityapi satyam .
6_1713 kintu ahaM gRhadAːhasya kartAː nAːsmi .
6_1714 vastutaH eːteː sarveː aBiyuktAːH santi .
6_1715 eːtEːH mama hAːniH pUːraNIːyAː.
6_1716 DanaruciH abravIːt-gRhadAːhasya sAːkSAːt kAːraNaM kiM vartateː .
6_1717 gRhapAːlaH itastataH aDAːvat .
6_1718 tasmAːt agniH gRhasya sarveːSu BAːgeːSu prAːrasat .
6_1719 kiM gRhapAːlaH teːna pAːdeːna aDAːvat yasmin pAːdeː tEːlAːrdreːNa kAːrpAːseːna yuktaM vastraKaNxaM badDam.
6_1720 na tat saMBavati iti spaSqameːva .
6_1721 gRhapAːlaH anyEːH triBiH pAːdEːH agniM sarveːSu gRhaBAːgeːSu prasAːrayitum azaknoːt yeːSAːM rakSakAːH mama BrAːtaraH santi .
6_1722 atasteː eːva gRhadAːhasya kartAːraH .
6_1723 tEːreːva mama hAːniH pUːraNIːyAː .
6_1724 tatoː nyAːyAːDIːzeːna upagataH .
6_1725 ataH saH banDanAːd moːcitaH .
6_1726 nyAːyAːDIːzeːna trayoːH BrAːtaraH AːjYAːpitAːH-pUːrayata DanaruceːH hAːnim.
6_1727 ataH tat cUːrNam aBuktvAː eːkasmin mRdGaqeː saYcinoːti sm .
6_1728 mRdGaqaH BagnaH goːDUːmacUːrNaM ca BUːmOː vikSiptam .
6_1729 udyAːneːSu zAːlIːmAːra-nizAːta iti dveː udyAːneː prasidDeː manoːrameː ca staH .
6_1730 atra janAːH zikAːrAː iti nOːkayAː jalavihAːraM kurvanti prasannAːH ca Bavanti .
6_1731 eːSa Kalu duSqamahoːragakulAːvAːsaH.
6_1732 pazyantu BavatyaH.
6_1733 vRdDagoːpAːlakaH - hAː BartaH! eːSa kanyakAːBiH vAːryamAːNoː yamunAːhradaM praviSqaH .
6_1734 mAː Kalu mAː Kalu sAːhasaM kRtvAː praveːSqum .
6_1735 atra vyAːGrAː varAːhAː hastinaH pAːnIːyaM pIːtvAː tatrEːva mriyanteː .
6_1736 kaTaM na dRzyateː.
6_1737 kimidAːnIːM karoːmi.
6_1738 Bavatu, imaM tAːvat kumBapalAːzamAːrUːhya niDyAːyAːmi.
6_1739 hAː hAː DUːma utTitaH.
6_1740 saMkarSaNaH pazyantu BavatyaH
6_1741 vRdDagoːpAːlakaH- hIː hIː sAːDu BartaH! sAːDu!.
6_1742 kAːliyasya paYca PaNAːn
6_1743 dAːmoːdaraH-kAːliya! kimarTamidAːnIːM yamunAːhRdaM
6_1744 kAːliyaH -prasIːdatu Bagavan ! ajYAːnAːd atikrAːntavAːn , sAːntaHpuraH zaraNAːgatoː$smi.
6_1745 tadicCAːmi garuwAːdaBayaM BagavatprasAːdAːt.
6_1746 dAːmoːdaraH -aneːna baleːna BavAːn garvitaH.
6_1747 dAːmoːdaraH - pravizatu BavAːn.
6_1748 tadidAːnIːmeːva viSaM saMhratya yamunAːhradAːd niSkrAːmAːmi.
6_1749 satyameːva jayateː BAːratasya AːdarzavAːkyam asti .
6_1750 asya rAːSqriyaH DvajaH trirawgam asti .
6_1751 janagaNamana eːtasya rAːSqragAːnam vandeː mAːtaram rAːSqragIːtam ca asti .
6_1752 BAːratasya rAːjaDAːnIː dillIː asti .
6_1753 dIːpAːvalIː BAːratavarSasya eːkaH mahAːn utsavaH astti .
6_1754 ayam utsavaH kAːrtika-mAːsAːsya amAːvasyAːyAːm Bavati .
6_1755 idam kaTyateː yat rAːvaNam hatvAː rAːmaH asmin eːva divaseː sIːtayAː lakSmaNeːna ca saha ayoːDyAːm prati AːgacCat .
6_1756 tadAː ayoːDyAːyAːH janAːH atIːva prasannAːH aBavan .
6_1757 ataH teː svAːni gRhAːNi dIːpAːnAːm mAːlAːBiH Aːloːkayan .
6_1758 tataH praBRti prativarSam tasmin eːva divaseː eːSaH utsavaH Bavati .
6_1759 sarveː janAːH svagRhAːNi svacCAːni kurvanti, suDayAː limpanti sundarEːH ca citrEːH BUːSayanti .
6_1760 teː sva-mitreːByaH banDuByaH ca miSqAːnnam preːSayanti .
6_1761 bAːlakAːH bAːlikAːH ca krIːxanakAːnAːm miSqAːnnAːnAːm sPoːqaka-padAːrTAːnAːm ca krayaNam kurvanti .
6_1762 sAːyaMkAːleː sarveː janAːH dIːpAːnAː mAːlAːH prajjvAːlayanti .
6_1763 dIːpAːnAːm prakAːzaH anDakAːram apanayati .
6_1764 puruSAːH striyaH bAːlakAːH bAːlikAːH ca nUːtanAːni vastrAːNi DAːrayanti AːpaNAːnAːm ca zoːBAːm draSqum gacCanti .
6_1765 rAːtrOː janAːH lakSmIːm pUːjayanti miSqAːnnAːni ca BakSayanti .
6_1766 BAːratIːyAːH imam utsavam prativarSam soːllAːsam samAːyoːjayanti .
6_1767 gawgAː parvatarAːjahimAːlayAːt praBavati .
6_1768 eːSAː sarvAːsu nadIːSu zreːSVAː pavitratamAː ca asti .
6_1769 gawgAːyAːH udBavaviSayeː eːkAː kaTAː asti .
6_1770 BagIːraTaH nAːma nRpaH pUːrvajAːnAːm udDAːrAːya tapasyAːm akaroːt tapasyAːyAːH ca praBAːveːNa saH gawgAːM svargAːt DarAːyAːm avatAːrayituM samarTaH aBavat .
6_1771 ataH eːva imAːM janAːH BAːgIːraTIː iti api kaTayanti .
6_1772 teː asyAːH jalam atyaDikaM pAːvanaM manyanteː .
6_1773 bahavaH zradDAːlujanAːH pratidinam asyAːM snAːnaM kurvanti imAːM ca pUːjayanti .
6_1774 asyAːH taqeː haridvAːra-RSikeːSa-prayAːga-vAːrAːNasIː-ityAːdIːni aneːkAːni tIːrTasTAːnAːni santi .
6_1775 prativarSaM puNyeːSu parvasu lakSAːNi janAːH eːSu tIːrTasTAːneːSu Aːgatya asyAːH pAːvanajaleːna snAːnaM kRtvAː duritAːni dUːrIːkurvanti .
6_1776 yantrakAːrAːH asyAːH jalamavarudDya seːtuM badDvAː mahAːjalAːSayeːSu jalasaYcayaM kurvanti .
6_1777 eːvaM prakAːreːNa saYcitaM jalaM kSeːtrAːNAːM siYcanAːya upayujyateː .
6_1778 aneːna BUːmiH urvarAː Bavati praBUːtaM ca annam utpAːdayati .
6_1779 eːvaM gawgAːyAːH jalaM kRSeːH mahAːntam upakAːraM karoːti .
6_1780 asyAːH jaleːna vidyut api utpannAː Bavati .
6_1781 iyaM dUːradarzana-DvanivikSeːpaka-zIːtakEːtyAːdIːni yantrAːNi saYcAːlayati viviDAːnAːM ca paNyAːnAːM vastUːnAːM nirmAːNeː sahAːyikAː Bavati .
6_1782 eːvaM gawgAː loːkaM paraloːkaM ca uBayam api upakaroːti .
6_1783 gRDramAːrjAːra kaTAː asyAːH krIːxAːyAːH vartamAːnaM svarUːpaM eːkamaSqaSaqtriNi tameː varSeː nizcitam aBUːt .
6_1784 uBayoːH pakSayoːH pratyeːkaM pakSeː eːkAːdaza krIːxakAːH BavantIːtyeːtat tu eːkamaSqasaptazUːnyam tameː varSeː nirDAːritam aBavat .
6_1785 eːtatsambanDinIː antAːrAːSqriyasaMsTAː eːkamnavazUːnyamcatvAːri tameː varSeː pratiSVAːpitAː .
6_1786 adyatveː eːSAː krIːxAː vizveː atyantam loːkapriyAː vartateː .
6_1787 pAːdakandukakrIːxAːyAːH vizvapratiyoːgitAː eːkamnavatriNizUːnyam tameː varSeː prAːrabDAː .
6_1788 eːkamnavaaSqaaSqa tamasya varSasya jUːna julAːIːmAːsayoːH PrAːMsadeːzasya rAːjaDAːnyAːM pEːrisanagareː pAːdakandukakrIːxAːyAːH yAː vizva pratiyoːgitAː aBavat tasyAːH saMkSiptaM vivaraNam atra prastUːyateː .
6_1789 teːSu deːzeːSu jarmanIː -iqalIː -arjeːnqIːnAː- xeːnamAːrka -ityeːtAːn deːzAːn kramazaH parAːjitya kroːziyAː -PrAːMsa -hAːlEːNxa -brAːjIːla ityeːteː catvAːroː deːzAːH vizvapratiyoːgitAːyAː upAːntimacaraNeː praviSqAː aBavan .
6_1790 dvitIːyAː sparDAː brAːjIːla-hAːlEːNxa deːzayoːH maDyeː aBavat .
6_1791 praTamAːyAːM sparDAːyAːM kroːziyAː- deːzasya - xeːvara- sUːkAː- nAːmakeːna krIːxakeːna pUːrvam eːkaM goːlaM kRtam .
6_1792 eːtadanantaraM kroːziyAː deːzasya daleːna AːtmarakSAːyEː mahAːn prayatnaH kRtAːH .
6_1793 asmin prayatneː kroːziyAː deːzasya krIːxakAːH PrAːMsadeːzIːyAːn krIːxakAːn vAːrayituM maDyAːntaraM yAːvat saPalAː aBavan dvitIːyeː kAːlAːrDeː liliyana-Turam-nAːmakeːna PrAːMsa-deːzasya krIːxakeːna goːlAːdvayaM kRtam.
6_1794 eːvaM PrAːMdeːzIːyakrIːxAːdaleːna kroːziyAːdeːzasya krIːxAːdalaM parAːjitam.
6_1795 dvitIːyAːyAːM sparDAːyAːM brAːjIːla -hAːlEːNxa- deːzOː nirDAːritasamayeː eːkEːkaM goːlaM kRtvAː tulyOː AːstAːm .
6_1796 hAːlEːNda- krIːxAːdalataH pEːqrika-klUːvaranAːmakeːna krIːxakeːna brAːjIːla deːzasya ca roːnEːlxoː nAːmakeːna prasidDeːna krIːxakeːna eːkEːkaM goːlaM kRtam.
6_1797 atirikta-samayeː$pi uBayoːH koː$pi pakSoː na parAːjitaH .
6_1798 pEːnalqIː -pAːdAːGAːteːSu brAːjIːla-deːzIːyeːna krIːxAːdaleːna hAːlEːNxadeːzasya krIːxAːdalaM parAːjitam .
6_1799 pratiyoːgitAːyAːH antimacaraNeː PrAːMsa- brAːjIːladeːzayoːH maDyeː sparDAː aBavat .
6_1800 sparDAːyAːH prAːgeːva brAːjIːladeːzasya prasidDaH roːnEːlxoːnAːmAː krIːxakaH AːkarSeːNa AːkrAːntoː$Bavat .
7_1801 asya eːkasmin pAːdeː pIːxAː$pi AːsIːt .
7_1802 parameːtasyAːmapi avasTAːyAːM brAːjIːladeːzasya krIːxAːdalasya neːtAː taM svakIːyeː daleː viDRtavAːn .
7_1803 eːSa nirNayaH yuktoː nAːsIːt .
7_1804 asvasTatAːyAːH heːtoːH roːnEːlxoː sparDAːsamayeː krIːxAːkSeːtrAːt gamanAːgamanamakaroːt .
7_1805 goːlakaraNasya ca svarNAːvasaramapi prAːpya goːlaM kartuM nAːzaknoːt .
7_1806 eːteːna brAːjIːladeːzasya krIːxakAːnAːm eːkAːgratAː BagnAː saMjAːtAː AːtmavizvAːsazca vyanazyat .
7_1807 PrAːMsadeːzasya krIːxakAːH eːtAːdRzIːM sTitiM vIːkSya DyAːneːna kOːzaleːna ca brAːjIːladeːzasya krIːxAːdalasya aBiBavituM samarTAː aBavan .
7_1808 PrAːMsadeːzIːyadalasya neːtAː jiMdeːnamahoːdayaH zirasAː goːladvayaM kRtavAːn .
7_1809 avaziSqeːSu kSaNeːSu imEːnuala -pEːqiqa-nAːmakeːna krIːxakeːna kuzalatayAː tRtIːyamapi goːlaM kRtam .
7_1810 PrAːMsadeːzeːna trIːNi goːlAːni kRtAːni .
7_1811 brAːjIːladeːzasya upalabDistu zUːnyAː AːsIːt .
7_1812 eːvaM pUːrva vijeːtAːraM brAːjIːladeːzaM parAːjitya PrAːMsadeːzaH pAːdakandukavizvapratiyoːgitAːyAːM vijeːtAː aBavat .
7_1813 dvOː unmattOː AːmravRkSam Aːruhya tasya zAːKAːyAːM lambamAːnOː AːstAːm .
7_1814 kiYcit kAːla anantaraM tayoːH anyataraH aDaH nyapatat .
7_1815 tadAː aparaH tam apRcCat-.
7_1816 kiM BavAːn zrAːntaH jAːtaH.
7_1817 na hi BrAːtaH! pakvaH jAːtaH .
7_1818 aparaH uttaram uktavAːn .
7_1819 aDyAːpakaH - saptAːhaH vyatIːtaH ,tvaM vidyAːlayaM na AːgataH.
7_1820 CAːtra:- zrIːman ! mama svAːsTyaM samyak na AːsIːt .
7_1821 aDyAːpakaH - astu .
7_1822 kintu zvaH cikitsakAːt pramAːNapatram Aːnayatu.
7_1823 CAːtraH- zrIːman! BavAːn tasya sTAːneː paYca rupyakAːNi arTadaNxam eːva svIːkaroːtu.
7_1824 cikitsakaH tu vEːdyakIːyapramAːNapatrasya kRteː paYcAːzat rupyakAːNi gRhNAːti.
